msgid ""
"Search for similar issues on the package's issue tracker. Django Debug "
"Toolbar’s is `on GitHub <https://github.com/jazzband/django-debug-toolbar/"
"issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+sort%3Aupdated-desc>`_."
